    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特色</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《真·女神转生Ⅴ》的决定版</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全球累计销量超过100万套，ATLUS引以为傲的RPG游戏《真·女神转生Ⅴ》在系统和剧情等诸多方面全面升级后，于多个本世代主机上登场！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作在《真·女神转生Ⅴ》游戏系统基础上对一般区域探索、恶魔对话、战斗、成长要素等诸多方面进行了细致改进，还增加了新的恶魔体验等新要素！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏更加易于上手，游玩体验进一步提升。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作故事仍然拥有多种结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可谓是《真·女神转生Ⅴ》的决定版！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875830/extras/19af89335ac1899a8a59bcc88d92c225.poster.avif?t=1763530264\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875830/extras/19af89335ac1899a8a59bcc88d92c225.webm?t=1763530264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875830/extras/721da23d1157f3080d439d7ecd9cfbc3.poster.avif?t=1763530264\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875830/extras/721da23d1157f3080d439d7ecd9cfbc3.webm?t=1763530264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >创世还是复仇？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏开篇时，玩家需在两种路线中做出选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分别为“创世女神篇”和“复仇女神篇”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两条路线的初期剧情相同，随后故事走向渐渐发生变化，到游戏中期剧情会出现显著差异。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最终两条路线将迎来截然不同的结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创世和复仇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请尽情体验这两个故事吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※“创世女神篇”的故事和《真·女神转生Ⅴ》中的相同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875830/extras/d2399e3b97d1a6c98924699ddae01863.poster.avif?t=1763530264\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875830/extras/d2399e3b97d1a6c98924699ddae01863.webm?t=1763530264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >恶魔种类超过270种</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了《真·女神转生Ⅴ》中的恶魔，本作中还增加了由角色设计师土居政之新绘制的恶魔，以及过往作品中的恶魔，总计超过270种恶魔即将登场！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中不仅可通过对话来使恶魔成为我方的一员，还可让恶魔们互相融合，从而创造出新的恶魔。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您将享受到极致的恶魔体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875830/extras/14b9dd583a88a6d622f61118e87a07c6.poster.avif?t=1763530264\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875830/extras/14b9dd583a88a6d622f61118e87a07c6.webm?t=1763530264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
